message.body: Gaaabbbiiii, tonight I'm making plans to see you, duh! All I've got to do today is laundry (and to not go to bed too late because I work early tomorrow.)
Oh I haven't been to the movies in ages! I actually just got home and am about to go do my laundry, I'll call you when I'm done with it?
Half an hour left on the dryer!
Cool! Theres a 645 or 905 at roxy, we should get food before, or I can cook if we do the 905
Yay! Let's do the 6:45 if we can manage? I've got work at 6:30 in the morn woohoo!
Gabi sorry I swanned off so quick to bed last night without saying bye, haha. I was so glad to see you! Let's make a sci fi Friday list soon? Maybe at my house so I can be a Decatur ambassador?
Das ok! So good to see you too. I started a list on a google doc, whats ur email adress these days? Should we start this friday?
